title: Holidays At The Museum Cards
description:
This box of notecards features a contemporary illustration of The Art Institute of Chicago’s entrance flanked by the famous Edward Kemeys Lions, wreathed for the holiday season.

The cards are made from a sustainable FSC certified mix paper and vegetable-based inks.

  • Card dimensions: 5 x 7 in.
  • Box dimensions: 5.625 x 7.625 x 1.375 in.
  • 20 cards and envelopes.
  • Interior message:  Happy Holidays
